# Trikonam website — environment variables.
#
# The Journal reads from Sanity when these are set. Leave them empty and the Journal
# transparently falls back to the local seed content (the site still builds and works).
#
# After creating your Sanity project (see docs/JOURNAL_CMS.md), copy this file to
# `.env.local` for local builds and add the same values to the Cloudflare Pages
# environment variables so production builds source the Journal from Sanity.

NEXT_PUBLIC_SANITY_PROJECT_ID=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SANITY_DATASET=production
NEXT_PUBLIC_SANITY_API_VERSION=2024-01-01
